{{!
    @template mod_scorecard/previous_attempt_callout

    Compact summary of the previous attempt rendered above the form on retake.

    Context variables required:
    * headline  - Lang string retake:previousattempt:headline.
    * body      - Lang string retake:previousattempt:format (already substituted).

    Example context (json):
    {
        "headline": "Most recent attempt",
        "body": "1 January 2026, 18 / 30, Strong"
    }
}}
<div class="scorecard-previous-attempt-callout alert alert-info">
    <strong>{{{headline}}}</strong> &mdash; {{{body}}}
</div>
